_sText: This was in the Maps in Progress Section, but after going over it, I think the only thing I might change in the future would be the textures. This is not a final release, but as close to the final as I think I might get with this one. This map (gg_trench) features two small towers across from a large double trench with a bridge over it. There are tunnels connecting the towers through the trenches and another approach from underground. My map has many different height/distance approaches for those who favor sniping, camping, rushing, and dying. If you can think of any improvements to the overall look or the gameplay, let me know. Thanks. **UPDATE** Okay, I could only make 24 player spawns. Per team. If you can find a way to run/host a 48 man game, feel free to use this map.
